last_episode_to_air.name: The Alpha and the Omega
last_episode_to_air.overview: The future of Krypton is at stake as Seg faces off against his enemy, General Zod, with the help of his allies.

name: Krypton
overview: Set two generations before the destruction of the legendary Man of Steel’s home planet, Krypton follows Superman’s grandfather — whose House of El was ostracized and shamed — as he fights to redeem his family’s honor and save his beloved world from chaos.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Superman's grandfather, Seg-El, learns Krypton is in danger of being destroyed so that his future grandson will never be born.

episodes.name: House of El
episodes.overview: After suffering a tragedy, Seg must adjust to a new life, a new rank and a new threat.

episodes.name: The Rankless Initiative
episodes.overview: During a military crackdown on Seg's home district, Seg and Adam Strange race to find a deadly Sentry.

episodes.name: The Word of Rao
episodes.overview: Seg is approached by a Black Zero leader as Rao finds a scapegoat for the failed Rankless Initiative.

episodes.name: House of Zod
episodes.overview: Jayna grapples with her torn loyalties as Seg fights for survival within the heart of Black Zero.

episodes.name: Civil Wars
episodes.overview: Seg is faced with an impossible choice that will shape the El legacy and the fate of the universe.

episodes.name: Transformation
episodes.overview: After a failed coup, Daron punishes the conspirators. Lyta and Dev go in search of Jayna.

episodes.name: Savage Night
episodes.overview: A resistance movement begins to form to impede the Voice of Rao's increasing power and influence.

episodes.name: Hope
episodes.overview: Seg must decide if he can make the ultimate sacrifice in service of the greater good of Kandor.

episodes.name: The Phantom Zone
episodes.overview: Seg races to save his city from being overtaken as the bottling of Kandor begins.

episodes.name: Light-Years from Home
episodes.overview: Seg-El is stranded far from home, where his grandfather leads a rebellion against General Zod.

episodes.name: Ghost in the Fire
episodes.overview: Adam Strange and Seg evade a bounty hunter, while General Zod uses Nyssa to further his cause.

episodes.name: Will to Power
episodes.overview: The Rebels gain advantage against General Zod, as Seg goes head-to-head with Brianiac.

episodes.name: Danger Close
episodes.overview: Seg and Adam return to a very different Kandor. Val and his Rebels prepare a major offensive.

episodes.name: A Better Yesterday
episodes.overview: Amidst a hostage negotiation that could end the war on Krypton, Seg seeks answers about Lyta.

episodes.name: In Zod We Trust
episodes.overview: In the wake of tragedy, Seg helps Nyssa rescue their son. Alliances on Wegthor fracture.

episodes.name: Zods and Monsters
episodes.overview: General Zod pushes for control of a dominating weapon. Seg and Nyssa fight to save Seg's life.

episodes.name: Mercy
episodes.overview: Dev and Jayna help Seg and Nyssa target General Zod's fleet, when they make a shocking discovery.

episodes.name: Blood Moon
episodes.overview: Zod brings Doomsday to heel and unleashes him on the Rebels, and Seg, Val, and Kem fight a last-ditch battle to hold the creature back while their compatriots escape.

episodes.name: The Alpha and the Omega
episodes.overview: The future of Krypton is at stake as Seg faces off against his enemy, General Zod, with the help of his allies.
